{"type": "article", "id": 47542, "title": "卷纸般的便利贴，拿来记录身边小事很不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-11-23T23:18:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 45756, "name": "产皮设计"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 45757, "name": "ANICORN"}, {"id": 45758, "name": "Gantri"}, {"id": 32871, "name": "Fort Standard"}, {"id": 41344, "name": "George & Willy"}, {"id": 31325, "name": "Chilewich"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 250, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171123195613vYV7GOUcj2alBkCh.jpeg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Roxanne armchair by Michael Young for Gufram</h3><p>Roxanne 是 The Police 乐队的一首代表作，设计师 Michael Young 以此为灵感设计了一把同名扶手椅，与其合作的是意大利制造商 Gufram，内里由聚氨酯泡沫制成，是符合人体工程学的友好设计。Roxanne 最大的特点是两侧有凹槽，称为 The Tube，可以收纳钱包、手机或者文件，设计师称放在餐厅、酒店大堂和休息室皆可。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195656hSKN7WeV0r9yYI5H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195656WwROnt8jTfu1DI9S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195657bCncfgypQo7x2q6D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195706G04sWlnhQ8rLZ9AC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195716gZQ5nmhiTB48uRKO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://design-milk.com/roxanne-innovative-armchair-inspired-music/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Blocks EDITIONS Placemats by Chilewich</h3><p>创立于 1997 年的美国餐垫品牌 Chilewich，创始人是具有艺术家背景的Sandy Chilewich，如果用一句话概括目前的生意是：“每周生产 4 万张垫子，收入 3500 万美元”。</p><p>最近他们发布的 Chilewich EDITIONS 系列，希望能够改变你的桌面风格，各种素雅的、相近色系的颜色被组合在一起，大小不一，有方有窄，以黑色的线条划分成不同的色块，创造出极具艺术感的几何视觉效果，也为餐桌添入了别致的情趣。售价 60 美元，<a href=\"http://www.chilewich.com/store/table/editions/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195802MEHPxyVBRjpfqmkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.743333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195803Ql7IDW3v9NzO4nm2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195804XD9AMBEh8t6upCeG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195809MQ1gI3bzhNT4lFG0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Chilewich</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Daily Roller from George &amp; Willy</h3><p>这是一款壁挂式的滚筒便利贴，运作原理类似于卫生间的卷筒纸。在设计师看来，无论是待办清单，头脑风暴的各种想法，还是对一件事的优劣评估，都需要一个随手可以方便写下来的地方，这是表达想法最简便易行的方式。</p><p>George &amp; Willy 把它做成了滚筒的样式，更添趣味，又可以作为墙面装饰，既适合放在厨房写菜谱或购买清单，也可以放置在办公室记录待办事项，或者突然而至的灵感，适合任何人使用。售价 120 美元，提供黑白两色选择，<a href=\"https://portofraleigh.co/collections/living/products/daily-roller\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195839eUgk9HayQc1jG3LI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195839u0w9hfS2vWMOLGUI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711231958413Nu4caLsvwmI0pyd.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195841YZge6wrQqy7iW08P.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195842sJRtv1kZdmuQYOXD.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://portofraleigh.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">portofraleigh.co</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Solid Brass Fire Kit by Fort Standard</h3><p>你可能偶尔会遇到需要火柴的时候，但如今火柴不像过去那样是家中日常备用的物品。它也许被扔进抽屉后变潮，不再能够使用。Fort Standard 团队为火柴设计了一个保护壳套装，是一个漂亮的圆柱体黄铜罐，它不仅能够保持火柴干燥可用的性能，底部还有一个擦花垫，确保你随时取用方便。售价 84.96 美元，<a href=\"https://shop.coolmaterial.com/products/fort-standard-match-kit-in-brass\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195940gxISWOX1kM8Yb4eU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195941j7wkNhnMVHpWdiBE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123195941taSjcZ85xUyhzK6D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://shop.coolmaterial.com/products/fort-standard-match-kit-in-brass\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shop Cool Material</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Gantri 3D Printed Table Lamp</h3><p>Gantri 是旧金山一家初创公司，是一个有趣的专注于 3D 打印和按需制造的平台，他们将自己的用户描述为“未来主义的美学家”，这一系列 3D 打印的台灯，都具有可调节的 LED 光源，造型多样化，可以匹配不同的房间氛围。售价 148 美元，<a href=\"https://www.gantri.com/shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123200029qiJFKpTcd97eoz0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605469\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711232000352pcbk4ADK3MHzJEy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.106090\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711232000365UACQKFtNH83jyEO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.113131\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123200040vfTQRiez4sD86CYK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.248366\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Gantri</figcaption></figure></div><h3>ANICORN Series 000 Watch</h3><p>ANICORN 最新的 000 系列腕表主推优雅概念，搭配了灰色和玫瑰金的摩登组合，试图一改过往各种黑色调调的手表风格。表面处理得极为复杂，上面刻有 Dinamos 设计的瑞士字体数字，做了防水处理，由防反光蓝宝石水晶玻璃表面作为保护层。每秒钟、每分钟和每小时分别转动三个同心圆盘，但不会牺牲易读性。手表配有黑白色真皮表带，显得百搭且干练。售价 410 美元，<a href=\"https://www.anicorn-watches.com/products/anicorn-series-000-rosegold-gray-automatic-watches\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123200129nFcf32HIkSi0YCvE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711232001319sunNq2DRHQfUVLm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123200131T5z7hO8foUVl6Rx1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667174\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171123200132iVKL2MUS71G5JsrZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502568\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：ANICORN</figcaption></figure></div>"}